#### Rough Design Sketch.

Sketch via [tinkercad](https://www.tinkercad.com). Two lighting points, two of triple double gang sockets (with built in USB) and a doubel docket to power the telly.  Planning to use easybulb.com / limitlessled.com/ / mi-light to control the lights - hence no physical wired lighting switches. 

~~At the moment the limiting factor is the 6A MCB on my house's consumer unit that [feeds outside](https://imgur.com/a/RQNy2).~~ New plan, use a plug connected to an existing socket, not a fixed circuit under [part p](https://www.google.co.uk/search?q=part+p).   
