#### Run cable

The first step was to drill a hole, in a cavity wall - two brick thickness + air gap. Thanks to [Ben](https://twitter.com/dbrb2) for the loan of Drill and drill bit.  You not that the hole is downward, to reduce any water inlet.   I had some nice orange cable from [PVG](https://play.google.com/store/apps/developer?id=PVG&hl=en_GB). 
