text:

#### First Overhead Light

Using a [£3 Bulk Head](http://www.diy.com/departments/bq-taro-white-60w-mains-powered-bulkhead-wall-light/198569_BQ.prd) wall light with a bluetooth controlled LED lamp. See [Automation](../../automation/) for more details about the lights control.
