#### Finished

Did a big push and finished the rest of wiring within one evening. What made it so quick and simple were the [Wago Connectors](http://www.screwfix.com/p/3-way-lever-connector-222-series-pack-of-50/76776) - this video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_KhBoxgyXgI explains it well. Throw away your terminal block and use wago connectors. 
